PS1="[\[\033[32m\]\w]\[\033[0m\]\n\[\033[1;36m\]\u\[\033[1;33m\]$ \[\033[0m\]"

# I ssh this computer mainly to control some apps (amarok, vlc and such)
# so setting the default display simplify lots of commands
